Frederik Aust

Hi, Im a postdoctoral researcher in the Research Methods and Experimental Psychology group at the University of Cologne. I develop and test mathematical models of human cognition using Bayesian statistics and try to improve the computational reproducibility of psychological science. I also create R packages.

To find out more about me and my work,
have a look at my CV and the following links.
